Lɩmfala ana acɔlɔ kpɛɛɛ kaawɛ naayɩ nɛ payaɣ-yɛ se Lɩmfala lʊbɛ, nɛ aawɛ kacʊka kamaɣ fɛyɩ ɛlɛ pɩnzɩ 1982 taa lɩmfala ana  asɔɔ yem pɩlɩɩna alɩwaatʊ ndʊ pohuyi Iitayipuu lɩŋgamʊʊ yɔ.

